{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3b369f0a6","title":"关于西安事变应和平解决等事给图锡山的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ffefcdc843","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":16,"articleId":"b3b369f0a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"24b3015ed3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于西安事变应和平解决等事","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"d0eaf429f8","type":"paragraph","text":"给图锡山的信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"692b63c079","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月16日）飞送山西阁百川先生勋鉴：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"5635a23f30","type":"paragraph","text":"接彭雪峰（枫》转来电，知先生抗日救国义薄云天，敢方奉商各端，码荷赞谅，感幸实深。西安事变后，时局急转直下，有数事就商于先生者：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"34dd508675","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）时局应和平解决，万不宜再起内战，自速覆亡，散方删日通电详申斯旨，先生一言九鼎，敢气周旋宁陕之间，先停军事行动，再议时局善后","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"11d5bd3da4","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）当前急务抗日第一，抗日所急，在于援绥，请宜举宁方西进之军改道北进，张、杨二公所部无志切同仇，红军则久类，愿际骐尾与国优相见于绥察之间，共组抗日联军，推先生为统师，各军指挥调遗惟先生之命是从，给养方面以红军言所需甚少，但能发伙食费，即可不事征发，一切地方行政社会秩序不加丝毫干涉，气速指示以便遵循。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"20f2ba97f0","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）立即建立无线电联络，雪峰（枫》带去呼号密码，未知此处已否启用，敬方电台展叫未通，幸赐注意","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"},{"id":"6625900c1a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东十二月十六日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6"}],"page":{"id":"85fe486553","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"b3b369f0a6","start":176,"end":176}}}},"__N_SSG":true}